steps.instruction:
### Prep
- Preheat oven to 450F
- Set wire rack on a rimmed backing sheet
- Put drumsticks on the rack and season both sides generously with salt and pepper to taste

### Cooking Drumsticks
- Bake for 30 minutes
- Flip drumsticks and continue baking until golden and crisp (about 30 more minutes)

### Sauce
- Put apple juice, vinegar, soy sauce, honey, lemon zest, red pepper flakes and a pinch of salt into a large skillet
- Bring to a high simmer over medium-high heat.
- Cook until sauce is syrupy and coats the back of a spoon (about 20 to 25 minutes)
- Set aside until the chicken is done
- Stir the sesame seeds into the sauce, warm over medium heat.

### Combining
- Transfer the chicken to a large bowl
- Add the sauce and butter to the bowl
- Toss to coat
- Season with salt and pepper to taste

### Plating
- Put chicken on a  plate and drizzle any remaining sauce onto the chicken
